messages.content:
Based on the telemetry (metrics, traces, and logs) in the incident window, the failure was caused by a sustained traffic surge starting around 2024-01-24 02:09:00 UTC that produced resource saturation on ts-route-service (notably elevated CPU and increased disk I/O) which in turn caused downstream latency increases. The primary root cause is the high CPU usage on ts-route-service driven by the throughput spike.

```json
